<p>John and Dave are back from Macworld Expo and come out of the gate strong with this, the first Premium episode for February. They discuss using the Time Capsule as a shared network disk, capturing audio in various ways, your Mac&rsquo;s Stealth Mode, resetting and preventing duplicates with MobileMe and Time Travel sickness. Yep, that&rsquo;s right, you&rsquo;ll get all this &#8211; and more &#8211; in this week&rsquo;s Premium episode of Mac Geek Gab. Subscribe today for just US$25 for 6 months, download the episode, support your two favorite geeks, and enjoy!</p>
